# 📊 Excel Sales Analysis & Dashboard

## 📌 Overview

This project focuses on analyzing retail sales data using Microsoft Excel to uncover business insights and support data-driven decision-making. The analysis includes data cleaning, transformation, and visualization through an interactive dashboard.

---

## 🖼️ Dashboard Preview



---

## 🛠️ Tools Used

* Microsoft Excel
* Pivot Tables
* VLOOKUP
* Charts & Graphs
* Data Cleaning Techniques

---

## 🔍 Project Workflow

### 1. Data Cleaning

* Handled missing and inconsistent values
* Standardized data formats for analysis
* Ensured data accuracy using validation techniques

### 2. Data Analysis

* Created Pivot Tables to summarize large datasets
* Applied VLOOKUP for data mapping and integration
* Performed trend and category-wise analysis

### 3. Data Visualization

* Built charts to represent sales trends and performance
* Designed a dashboard for easy interpretation of KPIs
* Highlighted key metrics for business insights

---

## 📈 Key Insights

* Identified top-performing product categories contributing to overall revenue
* Analyzed sales trends across different time periods
* Discovered patterns in customer purchasing behavior
* Improved clarity in reporting through structured visualizations

---

## 🎯 Outcome

* Transformed raw data into meaningful insights
* Reduced manual analysis effort using Excel automation techniques
* Enabled faster and more effective decision-making

---

## 📂 Project Files

* Excel dataset and analysis file
* Dashboard and visualization outputs

---

## 🚀 Conclusion

This project demonstrates the use of Excel as a powerful tool for data analysis, visualization, and business reporting. It highlights the ability to work with real-world datasets and generate actionable insights.

